OL,3,CThree things we learned from the
OL,4,CRussell Findlay leader interview
OL,6,FITV Border will be sitting down with
OL,7,Fall the main political party leaders
OL,8,Fduring the Holyrood election campaign.
OL,10,FThe third interview was with the
OL,11,FScottish Conservative, Russell
OL,12,FFindlay. Here are three things we
OL,13,Flearned.
OL,15,FIndependence is still what gets him
OL,16,Fgoing
OL,18,FLittle has helped the Tories'
OL,19,Felectoral fortunes more since the 2014
OL,20,Findependence referendum than a battle
OL,21,Fover the constitution.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/17
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
