PN,35202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1776341451
OL,3,CThree things we learned from the
OL,4,CRussell Findlay leader interview
OL,6,FBut unlike his recent predecessors,
OL,7,FRussell Findlay has not been able to
OL,8,Frely on the issue as a means of
OL,9,Fboosting his own political stature.
OL,11,FIt has steadily slipped down the list
OL,12,Fof people's priorities as the
OL,13,FConservatives have tumbled down in the
OL,14,Fpolls.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/17
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1776341451
OL,3,CThree things we learned from the
OL,4,CRussell Findlay leader interview
OL,6,FThe other opposition parties to the
OL,7,FSNP ` Labour, the Liberal Democrat's
OL,8,Fand Reform ` aren't all that
OL,9,Finterested in engaging in the
OL,10,Fconstitutional question, partly
OL,11,Fbecause it usually does them more harm
OL,12,Fthan good with voters.
OL,14,FSo it's no surprise that Mr Findlay
OL,15,Fspies a gap in the market now that
OL,16,Ffirst minister John Swinney has said
OL,17,Fan SNP majority would be a mandate for
OL,18,Fa second referendum.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/17
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
