PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1776341451
OL,3,CThree things we learned from the
OL,4,CRussell Findlay leader interview
OL,6,FThe Scottish Tory leader says this
OL,7,Fwould be "a monumental waste of time
OL,8,Fand energy" and insists he's not just
OL,9,Fmaking that case to boost his own
OL,10,Fparty's flagging ratings.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/17
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1776341451
OL,3,CThree things we learned from the
OL,4,CRussell Findlay leader interview
OL,6,F"It's not a tactic. We are the
OL,7,FScottish Conservative and Unionist
OL,8,FParty and we can see and we know that
OL,9,Fin terms of economics, nowadays in
OL,10,Fparticular in terms of national
OL,11,Fsecurity, the thought of John
OL,12,FSwinney's SNP getting away with
OL,13,Fbreaking Scotland away, getting kicked
OL,14,Fout of Nato and putting us all in
OL,15,Fperil is the stuff of nightmares and
OL,16,Fthe stuff of madness."
OL,18,FMr Findlay suggested it might happen
OL,19,Fbecause Sir Keir Starmer is a "weak"
OL,20,Fprime minister.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/17
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
