PN,35206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1776341451
OL,3,CThree things we learned from the
OL,4,CRussell Findlay leader interview
OL,6,FSo, was Lord Cameron of Chipping
OL,7,FNorton ` then simply David Cameron `
OL,8,Flily-livered and wrong to agree to the
OL,9,F2014 vote?
OL,11,F"Look, the referendum took place
OL,12,Fbecause all parties agreed. That's
OL,13,Fwhat happened.
OL,15,F"It was the right thing to do and the
OL,16,Fpeople of Scotland said no thanks. And
OL,17,FI was a normal member of the public at
OL,18,Fthat point.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/17
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1776341451
OL,3,CThree things we learned from the
OL,4,CRussell Findlay leader interview
OL,6,F"I voted no and thought, naively, that
OL,7,Fwould be that and that the SNP might
OL,8,Feven begin to respect democracy. But
OL,9,Fthey never have."
OL,11,FIt may outwardly frustrate the
OL,12,FScottish Conservatives, but the
OL,13,Fcontinued push for independence gives
OL,14,Fthem a campaigning opportunity that
OL,15,Fthey are all too happy to exploit.
OL,17,FThere's no retreat to the
OL,18,Fsouth...honest!
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/17
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
