CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1776341452
OL,3,CThree things we learned from the
OL,4,CRussell Findlay leader interview
OL,6,FBefore Mr Findlay became a politician,
OL,7,Fhe delivered headlines as an
OL,8,Finvestigative journalist working for
OL,9,Ftitles including the Sunday Mail and
OL,10,FThe Sun.
OL,12,FHis reporting focused on organised
OL,13,Fcrime but he became the story just
OL,14,Fover ten years ago when sulphuric acid
OL,15,Fwas thrown in his face by a man on his
OL,16,Fdoorstep as part of a failed murder
OL,17,Fbid.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G12/17
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35213
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1776341452
OL,3,CThree things we learned from the
OL,4,CRussell Findlay leader interview
OL,6,FTwo days before the Christmas of 2015,
OL,7,FWilliam Burns disguised himself as a
OL,8,Fpostman and distracted Mr Findlay by
OL,9,Fasking him to sign a document before
OL,10,Flaunching the attack.
OL,12,FMr Findlay physically detained his
OL,13,Fattacker and avoided permanent
OL,14,Fscarring by quickly getting water onto
OL,15,Fhis face with the help of his
OL,16,Fneighbours.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G13/17
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35214
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1776341452
OL,3,CThree things we learned from the
OL,4,CRussell Findlay leader interview
OL,6,FIt was only after police arrested
OL,7,FBurns that Mr Findlay noticed the six-
OL,8,Finch serrated knife outside his home,
OL,9,Fwhich was presumably meant to end his
OL,10,Flife.
OL,12,FHe told me it was "a shocking,
OL,13,Fterrible, traumatising episode but one
OL,14,Ffrom which I was beyond lucky to
OL,15,Femerge unscathed".
OL,17,FThis all happened despite him having
OL,18,Ftaken precautions like never allowing
OL,19,Fhis photograph to appear beside his
OL,20,Fstories.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G14/17
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35215
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1776341452
OL,3,CThree things we learned from the
OL,4,CRussell Findlay leader interview
OL,6,FNow he is very much in the public
OL,7,Fdomain at a time when abuse of
OL,8,Fpoliticians is reaching record levels.
OL,10,FSo does he feel safe as an MSP?
OL,12,F"You just have to look at social media
OL,13,Fto see the abuse that is spouted at
OL,14,Fyou from usually cowardly anonymous
OL,15,Faccounts.
OL,17,F"So you are aware of the fact that
OL,18,Fbecause you're a politician of any
OL,19,Fcolour rosette there's a possibility
OL,20,Fpeople will take exception to you.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G15/17
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35216
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1776341452
OL,3,CThree things we learned from the
OL,4,CRussell Findlay leader interview
OL,6,F"I don't feel unsafe but I'm acutely
OL,7,Faware of my safety. I'm careful about
OL,8,Fwhat I do, where I go, not least
OL,9,Fbecause in my past life, the organised
OL,10,Fcrime groups that I wrote about,
OL,11,Fperhaps some of them regard business
OL,12,Fas being unfinished.
OL,14,F"But that's not to be alarmist ` but
OL,15,Fyou've got to be pragmatic."
OL,17,FSafety is sadly an issue all
OL,18,Fpoliticians have to take seriously but
OL,19,FMr Findlay knows more than most the
OL,20,Fdangers of putting your head above the
OL,21,Fparapet.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G16/17
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
